# SPEC §17.85 — the schema-snapshot files are compared byte-for-byte by
# `src/test/unit/adapters/persistence/wireSnapshots.test.ts`. The test
# emits LF via `JSON.stringify` regardless of platform, so the on-disk
# fixture MUST stay LF on all checkouts (Windows operators, Linux CI,
# macOS contributors). Without this rule, `core.autocrlf=true` on
# Windows would silently flip the files to CRLF in the working tree
# and the test would fail with a baffling whitespace-only diff.
src/test/snapshots/*.snap.json text eol=lf
